    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that it's complicated, but it feels like you're leaning more towards the idea that these laws are bad. if you had to weigh them, is the \"deterrence\" argument actually a valid sociological theory, or is it just an outdated way of thinking that most modern experts have moved past?",
